Package com.github.anastaciocintra.output

Class PrinterOutputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.OutputStream
      • java.io.PipedOutputStream
        • com.github.anastaciocintra.output.PrinterOutputStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, Flushable, AutoCloseable
    public class PrinterOutputStream
extends PipedOutputStream
    Supply OutputStream to the printer.

    PrinterOutputStream send data directing to the printer. The instance cannot be reused and the last command should be close(), after that, you need to create another instance to send data to the printer.
